to_s converts values to strings.
to_i converts values to integers (numbers.)
to_a converts values to arrays.

to get maxout of array
[15,15,30].max

to sort an array
[15,15,30].sort
[15,15,30].sort!-->makes that to apply on the array ticket

Replacing a word in a entire string
ticket['toast']='honeydew'


To reverse the line by line taking to arry
poem.lines.to_a.reverse-->here "bytes" or "chars" can also be used in place of "lines"


The above one made the 
poem.lines.to_a.reverse.join---->makes the reversed array to be join back to form the atring again







